<p class="jp">
        冬の太陽が京都の東山と渡月橋から昇る。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Sunrise" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The winter sun rises over Kyoto's eastern mountains and the Togetsu Bridge.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2502_A7R01610-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2502_A7R01610-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Hawaii Vibes・ハワイを感じる</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250214/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Hawaii Vibes・ハワイを感じる" /><published>2025-02-14T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-02-14T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/hawaii-vibes</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250214/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
        I came across this grove of palm trees in Arashiyama today, and although it's only a few degrees above freezing, I feel like I'm in Hawaii! Taken on Fujichome Provia 100F film.
</p>

<p class="jp">
        今日は嵐山でこのヤシの木立に出くわした。気温は氷点下数度しかないが、まるでハワイにいるような気分だ！
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Trees" /><category term="Film" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[I came across this grove of palm trees in Arashiyama today, and although it's only a few degrees above freezing, I feel like I'm in Hawaii! Taken on Fujichome Provia 100F film.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2502_A7R01992_ai.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2502_A7R01992_ai.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>